name: TextEditor
tagline: A simple text editor for the Nokia N9.
body: ![TextEditor](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6352990/11638945/4e0d3c48-9d32-11e5-8678-ade3cb12dd8c.png)TextEditor is a simple text editor application for the Nokia N9 phone. The application is released under the GPL3 license and the source codes are available on Github.
